CommandDoccommentNode.comment: Applies a monadic function to each element of an array, returning the array of results. The function is monomorphic: it is required to return a value of the same type. The internal implementation uses pointer equality, and does not allocate a new array if the result of each function call is pointer-equal to its argument. -/
